<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-9444] Incorrect exceptions handling from Splitter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-9444</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;br/&gt;
1. Create global onException handler&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;onException&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;exception&amp;gt;java.lang.Exception&amp;lt;/exception&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;handled&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;constant&amp;gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;/constant&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/handled&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;log message=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;SOME MESSAGE&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/onException&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. Create 2 routes with Splitter (set shareUnitOfWork to TRUE, important)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;route&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;from uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;timer:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//foo?repeatCount=1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
    &amp;lt;!-- Add some value list to body here --&amp;gt;

    &amp;lt;split shareUnitOfWork=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; stopOnException=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;simple&amp;gt;${body}&amp;lt;/simple&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;to uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;direct:handleSplit&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/split&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;

&amp;lt;route&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;from uri=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;direct:handleSplit&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;throwException ref=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;myException&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/route&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expected: string &quot;SOME MESSAGE&quot; is logged&lt;br/&gt;
Actual:  &amp;lt;log message=&quot;SOME MESSAGE&quot;/&amp;gt; is not executed at all &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;OS: Ubuntu 15.10&lt;br/&gt;
JDK: Oracle JDK 1.8.0_66&lt;br/&gt;
Camel version: 2.16.1&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
